HTTP Request Methods (HTTP so'rov usullari) 

1. GET
2. POST
3. PUT 
4. PATCH
5. DELETE

6. HEAD
7. CONNECT
8. TRACE
9. OPTIONS


1. GET, HEAD (Read)
2. POST (Add to collection) (to'plamga qo'shish)
3. PUT (Place, Repalce) (joylashtirish, almashtirish)
4. PATCH (Edit) (taxrirlash, o'gartirish)
5. DELETE (Delete) (o'chirish)
6. CONNECT (ulanish)
7. TRACE 
8. OPTIONS (variantlar)


HTTP Response Statuses (HTTP javob holatlari)

2xx - Success (muvaffaqiyatli)

3xx - Rediriction(qayta yo'naltirish)

4xx - client Errors (Client xatosi)

5xx - Server Errors (Server xatosi)



2XX 

200 - OK
201 - Created (yaratilgan)
202 - Accepted (Qabul qilingan)
203 - Non-Authorotative Information (Tasdiqlanmagan ma'lumolar)
204 - No Content (empty)
205 - Reset Content (tarkibni tiklash, (tozalash))
206 - Partial Content (qiaman tarib, (tarkibni qismi))
207 - Multi-Status (ko'o holatli)
208 - Alredy Reported (allaqachon xabar qilingan)
226 - IM Used (IM ishlatilgan)



4XX 

400 - Bad Request (noto'g'ri so'rov)
401 - Unauthorized (ruxsatsiz)
402 - Payment Required (to'lov talab qilanadi)
403 - Forbidden (taqiqlangan)
404 - Not Found (topilmadi)
405 - Method Not Allowed (method ruxsat etilmaydi)
406 - Not Acceptable (qabul qilib bo'lmaydi)
407 - Proxy Authentication Required (Proksi autentifikatsiyasi talab qilinadi)
408 - Request Timeout (so'rov muddati tugashi)
...
499 - Client Closed Request (clientning yopiq so'rovi)




5XX 

500 - Internal Server Error (serverdagi ichki xatolik)
501 - Not Implemented (amalga oshirilmagan)
502 - Bad Getaway ()
503 - Service Unavailable (service ish faoliyatida emas)
504 - Getaway Timeout ()
505 - HTTP Version Not Supported (HTTP versiyasi qo'llab-quvvatlanmaydi)
506 - Variant Also Negotiates ()
507 - Insufficient Storage (xotira yetarli emas)
508 - Loop detected (loop aniqlandi)
...
526 - Invalid SSL Certificate (yaroqsiz SSL sertifikati)




3XX 

300 - Multiple Choices (bir nechta tanlov)
301 - Moved Permanently (doimiy ko'chirildi)
302 - Moved Temporarily (vaqtinchalik ko'chirildi)
302 - Found (topildi)
303 - See Other (boshqasini ko'rish)
304 - Not Modified (o'zgartirilmagan)
305 - Use Proxy (proxy server foydalaning)
307 - Temporary Redirect (Vaqtinchalik qayta yo'naltirish)
308 - Parmament Redirect (Parmamentni qayta yo'naltirish) 